        <h1 id="page-title" class="title">
Asia-Pacific Broadcasting Union







        	
        (ABU)</h1>


<p style="font-style:italic;color:#666;margin-top:-20px;">Union de radiodiffusion pour l'Asie et le Pacifique<br /></p>
         
         <div style="float:right;width:400px;clear:right;margin-bottom: 40px;margin-left:40px;margin-top:10px;">
          	
         <iframe width="400" height="300" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;key=AIzaSyDSecKDTYLGmGVJj3bjqciTn48sZkHCEps&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Kuala Lumpur,+Malaysia&amp;z=9&amp;iwloc=A&amp;output=embed"></iframe>
<h2>Contact Details</h2>



		

	
	<p>Main address: SG: Javad Mottaghi<br />PO Box 12287 50772, <a href="/ybio?addcity_1_en=Kuala Lumpur" title="Kuala Lumpur (click to perform a search)">Kuala Lumpur</a>, <a href="/ybio?addpays_1_en=Malaysia" title="Malaysia (click to perform a search)">Malaysia</a><br />Tel: (60 3) 2282 3592<br />Fax: (60 3) 2282 4606<br />Email: <a title='Click to send an e-mail to this address (from your default e-mail client)' href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#694f4a5858594f4a505e4f4a58585f4f4a505e4f4a5859514f4a58595c4f4a505e4f4a5f5d4f4a505e4f4a50514f4a58585e4f4a5d5f4f4a5858584f4a58585d4f4a58595a4f4a5d5f4f4a5859504f4a585b58" target=_blank>natalia (at) abu.org.my</a><br /></p><p>Street Address: 2nd floor IPPTAR Bldg, Angkasapuri 50614, <a href="/ybio?addcity_1_en=Kuala Lumpur" title="Kuala Lumpur (click to perform a search)">Kuala Lumpur</a>, <a href="/ybio?addpays_1_en=Malaysia" title="Malaysia (click to perform a search)">Malaysia</a><br /></p><p>URL: <a title="Click to access page >http://www.abu.org.my/<" href="http://www.abu.org.my/" target="_blank">http://www.abu.org.my/</a><br /></p>		
		
<div style="clear:both;"><p> </p><p></p></div><p> </p>
</div>
         
<h2 style="margin-top:30px;">History</h2>
<p>1 July 1964, Tokyo (Japan), following 5 Asian Broadcasters' Conferences between 1957 and 1963. Statutes adopted at the last of these Conferences, 30 Sep-5 Oct 1963, Seoul (Korea Rep).</p>
<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Aims</h2>
<p>Assist in development of broadcasting <i>media</i> in the Asia/Pacific region; foster the use of these media in the cause of international understanding.</p>



	<div></div>

