<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Activities</h2>
<p>Knowledge management/information dissemination; guidance/assistance/consulting; events/meetings; awards/prizes/competitions.</p>


<h2 style="margin-top:20px;" id="ybp_structure">Structure</h2>
<p>General Assembly (annual); Administrative Council; Standing Committees (2); Study Groups and Working Parties; Secretariat. Maintains and operates: <a href="/s/or/en/1100045531" title="Asiavision (AVN)">Asiavision (AVN)</a>.</p>
	

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Languages</h2>
<p>English.</p>


<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Staff</h2>
<p>Over 30 paid.</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Financing</h2>
<p>Members' dues, in proportion to their operational budgets.</p>


<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Consultative Status</h2>
<p><a href="/s/or/en/1100027514" title="United Nations Economic and Social Council (ECOSOC)">United Nations Economic and Social Council (ECOSOC)</a> (Ros C); <a href="/s/or/en/1100010946" title="United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization (UNESCO)">United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization (UNESCO)</a> (Associate Status); <a href="/s/or/en/1100043851" title="Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (FAO)">Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (FAO)</a> (Special Status); <a href="/s/or/en/1100029679" title="World Intellectual Property Organization (WIPO)">World Intellectual Property Organization (WIPO)</a> (Permanent Observer Status).</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Relations with Inter-Governmental Organizations</h2>
<p>Observer to: <a href="/s/or/en/1100007048" title="Intergovernmental Committee of the International Convention of Rome for the Protection of Performers, Producers of Phonograms and Broadcasting Organizations">Intergovernmental Committee of the International Convention of Rome for the Protection of Performers, Producers of Phonograms and Broadcasting Organizations</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100025882" title="Union for the International Registration of Audiovisual Works">Union for the International Registration of Audiovisual Works</a>. Working relations with: <a href="/s/or/en/1100041183" title="International Telecommunication Union (ITU)">International Telecommunication Union (ITU)</a>. Sister union: <a href="/s/or/en/1100044130" title="Arab States Broadcasting Union (ASBU)">Arab States Broadcasting Union (ASBU)</a>; Invited to sessions of Intergovernmental Council of: <a href="/s/or/en/1100065387" title="International Programme for the Development of Communication (IPDC)">International Programme for the Development of Communication (IPDC)</a>. Together with UNESCO, instrumental in setting up <a href="/s/or/en/1100046899" title="Asia-Pacific Institute for Broadcasting Development (AIBD)">Asia-Pacific Institute for Broadcasting Development (AIBD)</a>. Links with: <a href="/s/or/en/1100010890" title="Asia-Pacific Telecommunity (APT)">Asia-Pacific Telecommunity (APT)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100035676" title="Telecommunication Development Bureau (BDT)">Telecommunication Development Bureau (BDT)</a>.</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Relations with Non-Governmental Organizations</h2>
<p>Member of: Digital radio mondial (DRM); <a href="/s/or/en/1100042430" title="World Broadcasting Unions (WBU)">World Broadcasting Unions (WBU)</a>; World DAB Forum. Organizes: <a href="/s/or/en/1100026818" title="World Conference of Broadcasting Unions">World Conference of Broadcasting Unions</a> together with sister unions: <a href="/s/or/en/1100066567" title="Caribbean Broadcasting Union (CBU)">Caribbean Broadcasting Union (CBU)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100002745" title="European Broadcasting Union (EBU)">European Broadcasting Union (EBU)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100026453" title="International Association of Broadcasting (IAB)">International Association of Broadcasting (IAB)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100001629" title="North American Broadcasters Association (NABA)">North American Broadcasters Association (NABA)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100030584" title="Organización de Telecomunicaciones Iberoamericanas (OTI)">Organización de Telecomunicaciones Iberoamericanas (OTI)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100031165" title="African Union of Broadcasting (AUB)">African Union of Broadcasting (AUB)</a>.<p> Links with:<p> <p>&nbsp;&bull; <a href="/s/or/en/1100067805" title="Asian Media Information and Communication Centre (AMIC)">Asian Media Information and Communication Centre (AMIC)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100050531" title="DVB - Digital Video Broadcasting Project">DVB - Digital Video Broadcasting Project</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100040740" title="International Academy of Broadcasting">International Academy of Broadcasting</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100063664" title="International Association of Broadcasting Manufacturers (IABM)">International Association of Broadcasting Manufacturers (IABM)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100014717" title="International Association of Women in Radio and Television (IAWRT)">International Association of Women in Radio and Television (IAWRT)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100065042" title="International Federation of Television Archives (IFTA)">International Federation of Television Archives (IFTA)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100029952" title="International Radio and Television Union (URTI)">International Radio and Television Union (URTI)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100025382" title="Organization of Asian-Pacific News Agencies (OANA)">Organization of Asian-Pacific News Agencies (OANA)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100055684" title="Pacific Telecommunications Council (PTC)">Pacific Telecommunications Council (PTC)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100056875" title="Public Broadcasters International (PBI)">Public Broadcasters International (PBI)</a>; <a href="/s/or/en/1100014124" title="Public Media Alliance (PMA)">Public Media Alliance (PMA)</a>.</p>

<h2 style="margin-top:20px;">Publications</h2>
<p><i>ABU News</i> (6 a year); <i>ABU Technical Review</i> (6 a year). Annual members' directory.</p>









